original_title: Fraggle Rock - Doin' Things That Doozers Do
overview: Red starts her own club, but only Cotterpin Doozer is interested; Cotterpin tries to convince the other Doozers to be friends with the Fraggles; and Cotterpin and Gobo Fraggle search for the original cave of the Doozers.
title: Fraggle Rock - Doin' Things That Doozers Do
